ror%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20Vaishali%20Adkane%20and%20her%20seven%20family%20members%20boarded%20the%20Neelkamal%20ferry%20at%20Gateway%20of%20India%20last%20afternoon%2C%20they%20had%20no%20clue%20they%20were%20about%20to%20have%20a%20near-death%20experience.%20About%2040%20minutes%20into%20the%20ferry%20ride%2C%20a%20Navy%20speedboat%20lost%20control%20and%20crashed%20into%20the%20vessel.%20At%20least%2013%20people%20have%20died%20and%20over%20100%20have%20been%20rescued.%20Fortunately%2C%20Vaishali%20and%20her%20family%20members%20have%20survived.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEight%20of%20us%20boarded%20the%20ferry%20at%20Gateway%20of%20India%20around%203%20pm.%20About%2040%20minutes%20later%2C%20a%20white%20speedboat%20crashed%20into%20the%20ferry.%20We%20all%20fell.%20The%20impact%20was%20such%20that%20one%20of%20the%20men%20on%20the%20speedboat%20landed%20inside%20our%20ferry.%20About%20five%20minutes%20later%2C%20people%20started%20shouting%20and%20telling%20us%20to%20wear%20life%20jackets.%20No%20one%20wore%20life%20jackets%20earlier.%20We%20felt%20we%20were%20going%20to%20die%2C%26quot%3B%20Vaishali%20told%20the%20media.%C2%A0She%20said%20people%20on%20the%20ferry%20started%20shouting%20for%20help%20but%20some%20vessels%20ignored%20them.%20%26quot%3BBut%20shortly%20after%2C%202-3%20boats%20came%20and%20started%20rescuing%20us.%20Thankfully%2C%20everyone%20in%20our%20family%20is%20safe.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20survivor%20Dinesh%20Adkane%20said%20the%20ferry%20was%20full.%20%26quot%3BI%20saw%20some%20people%20fall%20off.%20They%20screamed%20for%20help%2C%20but%20no%20one%20came%20for%2030%20minutes.%20After%20that%2C%20boats%20came%20and%20rescued%20us.%20At%20the%20time%20of%20the%20accident%2C%20no%20one%20was%20wearing%20life%20jackets.%20When%20the%20ferry%20started%20drowning%2C%20we%20were%20told%20to%20wear%20life%20jackets%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20dead%20are%2010%20civilians%20and%20thr