in%20the%20Brisbane%20Test.%20However%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ravichandran%20Ashwin%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1109-ravichandran-ashwin-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERavichandran%20Ashwin%3C%2Fa%3E's%20sudden%20decision%20to%20retire%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20series%20shocked%20everyone.%20Ashwin%2C%20one%20of%20the%20modern%20greats%20of%20the%20game%2C%20said%20goodbye%20to%20international%20cricket%20as%20the%20match%20concluded%2C%20leaving%20several%20questions%20unanswered.%20Ashwin%20did%20join%20India%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20press%20conference%20after%20the%20game%2C%20but%20didn't%20take%20any%20questions%20as%20he%20made%20his%20retirement%20decision%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20decision%20is%20indeed%20a%20shock%20to%20cricket%20lovers%20all%20across%20the%20globe%2C%20those%20closely%20following%20Ashwin%20on%20the%20cricket%20pitch%20knew%20that%20all%20wasn't%20well.%20A%20report%20in%20PTI%20explained%20the%20story%20behind%20Ashwin's%20decision%20to%20hang%20his%20boots%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20Border-Gavaskar%20Trophy%202024-25%2C%20including%20the%20role%20head%20coach%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20played.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20R%20Ashwin%20wasn't%20keen%20on%20flying%20to%20Australia%20if%20playing%20XI%20wasn't%20guaranteed.%20After%20India's%203-match%20Test%20series%20against%20New%20Zealand%20concluded%20with%20Rohit%20Sharma's%20men%20suffering%20a%200-3%20clean%20sweep%2C%20Ashwin%20started%20to%20wonder%20what's%20next%20for%20him.%20He%20even%20sought%20guarantees%20from%20selectors%20over%20playing%20XI%20selection%20on%20the%20tour%20of%20Australia.%20Certain%20guarantees%2C%20apparently%2C%20were%20given%20to%20him%20even%20as%20India%20picked%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Washington%20Sundar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C