h%20Social.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20would%20save%20massively%20on%20taxes%20and%20military%20protection.%20I%20think%20it%20is%20a%20great%20idea.%2051st%20State!!!%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftruthsocial.com%2F%40realDonaldTrump%2F113672861551554010%2Fembed%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20post%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20Trump%20has%20publicly%20mused%20at%20the%20idea%2C%20a%20joke%20that%20some%20have%20found%20in%20bad%20taste%2C%20particularly%20following%20the%20shock%20resignation%20of%20Canada's%20deputy%20prime%20minister%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Leger%20public%20opinion%20survey%20this%20week%20found%2013%20percent%20of%20Canadians%20support%20the%20notion%20of%20linking%20up%20with%20their%20southern%20neighbor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Trump%20made%20the%20same%20comment%20to%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20at%20a%20dinner%20at%20his%20Mar-a-Lago%20estate%20in%20Florida%20in%20late%20November%2C%20howls%20of%20laughter%20reportedly%20erupted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Fox%20News%2C%20Trump%20suggested%20that%20merging%20the%20two%20nations%20would%20not%20only%20resolve%20his%20concerns%20about%20fentanyl%20trafficking%2C%20over%20which%20he%20has%20threatened%20a%2025-percent%20tariff%20on%20Canadian%20goods%20but%20could%20also%20stem%20illegal%20immigration%20--%20an%20issue%20that%20mainly%20affects%20the%20US%20southern%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20suggestion%20raised%20eyebrows%20in%20Ottawa%20with%20some%20commenting%20that%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bnot%20funny%2C%26quot%3B%20humiliating%20and%20a%20not-so-subtle%20threat%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20incoming%20US%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20Trump%20has%20repeatedly%20referred%20to%20Trudeau%20in%20social%20media%20posts%20as%20the%20governor%20of%20Canada%20--%20a%20title%20used%20by%20leaders%20of%20the%2050%20US%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20jabs%20may%20have%20become%20more%20worrying%20for%20Canadians%20since%20the%20resignation%20of%20Deputy%20Prime%20Minister%20Chrystia%20Freeland%20this%20week%2C%20which%20spurred%20calls%20for%20Trudeau%20to%20quit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Boxer%20working%20a%20cut'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Trudeau%20advisor%20Gerald%20Butts%20reacted%20on%20social%20media%3A%20%26quot%3BTrump%20is%20like%20a%20boxer%20working%20a%20cut.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENorman%20Spector%2C%20an%20ex-staffer%20to%20former%20Canadian%20prime%20minister%20and%20Trump%20golfing%20buddy%20Brian%20Mulroney%2C%20wondered%20if%20Trump%20seriously%20wanted%20to%20annex%20the%20United%20States'%20northern%20neighbor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20will%20never%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20University%20of%20British%20Columbia%20politics%20professor%20Max%20Cameron%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNothing%20could%20be%20a%20greater%20impediment%20to%20Canada%20more%20closely%20integrating%20with%20the%20United%20States%20than%20Donald%20Trump%20in%20office%20in%20Washington%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20suspect%20this%20is%20all%20part%20of%20a%20pattern%20of%20bullying%20that%20is%20how%20he%20approaches%20negotiations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQueen's%20University%20professor%20Stephanie%20Chouinard%20echoed%20that%20view%2C%20saying%20Trump%20%26quot%3Bis%20taking%20advantage%20of%20the%20chaos%20in%20Canadian%20politics%20this%20week%20to%20further%20antagonize%20Trudeau.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPublic%20Safety%20Minister%20Dominic%20LeBlanc%20has%20insisted%20that%20despite%20Trump's%20teasing%2C%20he%20and%20Trudeau%20have%20had%20%26quot%3Bproductive%26quot%3B%20discussions%20with%20the%20president-elect%20and%20his%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20LeBlanc%20and%20Immigration%20Minister%20Marc%20Miller%20anno