to%20office%20on%20January%2020%20had%20an%20impact%20on%20the%20latest%20round%20of%20talks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20diplomatic%20source%20said%20that%20Hamas%2C%20isolated%20after%20the%20weakening%20of%20its%20Lebanese%20ally%20Hezbollah%20and%20the%20overthrow%20of%20Syrian%20strongman%20Bashar%20al-Assad%2C%20is%20keen%20to%20reach%20a%20deal%20before%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20people%20see%20(a%20deal)%20as%20the%20perfect%20Christmas%20gift%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20noted%20that%20since%20Hamas%20chief%20Yahya%20Sinwar's%20death%2C%20Hamas%20leaders%20abroad%2C%20known%20as%20more%20pragmatic%20than%20the%20mastermind%20of%20the%20October%207%2C%202023%20attack%20that%20sparked%20the%20war%2C%20have%20been%20conducting%20negotiations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20high-ranking%20Hamas%20official%20told%20AFP%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20the%20talks%20were%20at%20the%20%26quot%3Bfinal%20details%26quot%3B%20stage%20and%20that%20Qatar%20and%20Egypt%20would%20announce%20the%20agreement%20once%20negotiations%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20government%20spokesman%20David%20Mencer%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20proposed%20deal%20at%20a%20media%20briefing%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20stating%20%26quot%3Bthe%20less%20said%20the%20better%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20would%20the%20deal%20look%20like%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20their%20attack%20on%20Israel%20on%20October%207%20last%20year%2C%20Palestinian%20militants%20led%20by%20Hamas%20seized%20251%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENinety-six%20of%20them%20are%20still%20held%20in%20Gaza%2C%20including%2034%20the%20Israeli%20military%20says%20are%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20officials%20told%20AFP%20that%20the%20current%20framework%20for%20a%20deal%20would%20see%20the%20implementation%20of%20a%20ceasefire%20and%20the%20gradual%20release%20of%20hostages%20over%20three%20phases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%