the%20level%20remains%20%26quot%3Bsomewhat%20elevated%26quot%3B%20compared%20to%20the%20Fed's%20long-term%20target%20of%20two%20percent%2C%20Chair%20Jerome%20Powell%20told%20reporters%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20remained%20%26quot%3Bvery%20optimistic%26quot%3B%20about%20the%20state%20of%20the%20US%20economy%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20Fed%20was%20now%20%26quot%3Bsignificantly%20closer%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20end%20of%20its%20current%20easing%20cycle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20the%20final%20planned%20rate%20decision%20before%20outgoing%20Democratic%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20makes%20way%20for%20Republican%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20whose%20economic%20proposals%20include%20tariff%20hikes%20and%20the%20mass%20deportation%20of%20millions%20of%20undocumented%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20non-partisan%20Congressional%20Budget%20Office%20(CBO)%20estimates%20that%20imposing%20fresh%20tariffs%20would%20cut%20economic%20growth%20and%20push%20up%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20Trump's%20victory%20in%20November's%20election%2C%20some%20analysts%20had%20already%20pared%20back%20the%20number%20of%20rate%20cuts%20they%20expected%20in%202025%2C%20warning%20that%20the%20Fed%20may%20be%20forced%20to%20keep%20rates%20higher%20for%20longer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EInflation%20battle%20not%20over%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Fed%20has%20made%20progress%20tackling%20inflation%20through%20interest%20rate%20hikes%20in%20the%20last%20two%20years%20without%20dealing%20a%20knockout%20blow%20to%20either%20growth%20or%20unemployment%2C%20and%20recently%20began%20cutting%20rates%20to%20boost%20demand%20in%20the%20economy%20and%20support%20the%20labor%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20past%20months%2C%20the%20Fed's%20favored%20inflation%20measure%20has%20ticked%20higher%2C%20moving%20away%20from%20the%20bank's%20target%20and%20raising%20concerns%20that%20the%20inflation%20fight%20is%20not%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMembers%