ell-tuned%20for%20delivering%20clear%20speech.%20If%20you%20do%20find%20yourself%20needing%20an%20extra%20boost%2C%20the%20speech%20enhancement%20emphasizes%20dialogue%20even%20more%20without%20muddying%20explosions%20or%20altering%20other%20sound%20effects.%20It's%20impressive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20downside%2C%20the%20Arc%20Ultra%20is%20Sonos'%20most%20expensive%20soundbar%2C%20and%20it's%20disappointing%20that%20it%20doesn't%20support%20DTS%3AX%2C%20another%203D%20audio%20format%20that%20rivals%20Dolby%20Atmos.%20It%20also%20lacks%20HDMI%20video%20passthrough%2C%20so%20you%20can't%20use%20the%20bar%20to%20route%20extra%20devices%20to%20your%20TV%2C%20like%20a%20gaming%20console%20or%20streaming%20player.%20But%20these%20shortcomings%20are%20small%20compared%20to%20all%20the%20Arc%20Ultra%20gets%20right.%20If%20you%20want%20a%20single%2C%20powerful%20speaker%20in%20your%20living%20room%20that's%20capable%20of%20handling%20all%20your%20home%20theater%20needs%2C%20the%20Arc%20Ultra%20is%20the%20best%20Sonos%20soundbar%20there%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fsonos-arc-ultra-soundbar-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESonos%20Arc%20Ultra%20soundbar%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECheck%20out%20our%20guide%20to%20all%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-soundbar%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20soundbars%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2288a60d5c-4e2d-46d0-b0f9-735842308f7e%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20on%20a%20budget%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20on%20a%20budget%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Sonos%20Ray%20is%20the%20brand's%20most%20affordable%20and%20compact%20soundbar.%20Thanks%20to%20its%20minimal%20footprint%2C%20it's%20the%20best%20Sonos%20soundbar%20for%20bedrooms%20and%20apartments.%20For%20comparison%2C%20it's%20less%20than%20half%20the%20width%20of%20the%20Arc%20Ultra%20and%20a%20few%20inches%20shorter%20and%20less%20deep%20than%20the%20Beam%20(Gen%202).%20Despite%20its%20stature%2C%20it%20still%20far%20outdoes%20the%20capabilities%20of%20most%20speakers%20embedded%20in%20TV%20sets%2C%20especially%20lower-end%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20audio%20quality%2C%20you%20can%20expect%20a%20smooth%20experience%20that%20will%20bring%20any%20movie%20to%20life.%20You%20won't%20get%20the%20window-rattling%20lows%20or%20all%20of%20the%20flourishes%20offered%20on%20Sonos'%20pricier%20soundbars%2C%20but%20the%20Ray%20is%20impressive%20for%20its%20size%2C%20with%20a%20surprisingly%20detailed%20sound%20signature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222223%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Sonos%20Ray%20soundbar%20resting%20on%20a%20media%20console.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67633b96b1d5f0276b36ccea%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Sonos%20Ray%20delivers%20more%20expansive%20sound%20than%20we%20expected%20from%20such%20a%20small%20device.%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EStreaming%20music%20on%20the%20Ray%20over%20WiFi%20is%20great%2C%20too%2C%20offering%20better%20quality%20than%20a%20Bluetooth%20connection%20would%20provide.%20That%20said%2C%20it%20is%20a%20bummer%20that%20Sonos%20doesn't%20also%20include%20Bluetooth%20support%20as%20an%20alternative%20for%20those%20instances%20when%20WiFi%20might%20not%20be%20an%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ray%20is%20also%20a%20bit%20lacking%20in%20wired%20connectivity.%20It%20doesn't%20include%20an%20HDMI%20port%20and%20can%20only%20connect%20to%20a%20TV%20(or%20PC)%20via%20an%20optical%20cable.%20This%20does%20mean%20it%20has%20wide%20compatibility%20among%20older%20televisions%2C%20but%20it%20also%20means%20that%20it%20doesn't%20support%20lossless%20audio%20formats%2C%20Dolby%20Atmos%2C%20or%20automatic%20pairing%20with%20your%20TV%20remote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20plus%20side%2C%20you%20can%20still%20connect%20a%20Sonos%20subwoofer%20or%20rear%20Sonos%20speaker%20wirelessly%20to%20the%20Ray%20to%20boost%20its%20basic%20surround%20sound%20configuration.%20Like%20all%20Sonos%20soundbars%2C%20it%20also%20supports%20grouping%20with%20other%20Sonos%20speakers%20to%20create%20a%20multi-room%20audio%20setup%2C%20and%20it%20can%20pair%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fsonos-ace-headphones-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ESonos%20Ace%20headphones%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20so%20you%20can%20switch%20between%20soundbar%20and%20private%20listening%20with%20your%20TV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECheck%20out%20our%20guide%20to%20all%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-budget-soundbars%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20budget%20soundbars%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f37f8105-b8bc-438a-b222-b8af1ea80bc8%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20midrange%20model%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20midrange%20model%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Sonos%20Beam%20(Gen%202)%20serves%20as%20a%20middle%20ground%20between%20the%20brand's%20flagship%20Arc%20Ultra%20and%20its%20entry-level%20Ray.%20It's%20powerful%20enough%20to%20fill%20a%20medium-sized%20space%20with%20sound%20but%20isn't%20that%20much%20bigger%20than%20the%20Ray%2C%20so%20it%20can%20still%20work%20well%20in%20a%20bedroom%20or%20smaller%20living%20room.%20(That's%20where%20I've%20predominantly%20used%20the%20speaker.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20size%2C%20the%20midrange%20Beam%20really%20differentiates%20itself%20from%20the%20cheaper%20Sonos%20Ray%20by%20adding%20an%20HDMI%20eARC%20connection%20and%20support%20for%20Dolby%20Atmos.%20This%20means%20it%20can%20automatically%20work%20with%20many%20modern%20TV%20remotes%20and%20it%20has%20a%20wider%20sound%20stage.%20For%20under%20%24500%2C%20the%20Beam%20punches%20well%20above%20its%20weight%20class.%20It's%20a%20proper%20home%20theater%20in%20a%20box%2C%20perfect%20for%20most%20living%20rooms%20or%20other%20places%20that%20could%20use%20an%20audio%20upgrade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222223%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Sonos%20Beam%20resting%20on%20a%20media%20console%20under%20a%20TV%20and%20next%20to%20an%20Apple%20TV%20box.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F676312e55cddac6581d6b43c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Sonos%20Beam%20is%20a%20great%20fit%20for%20a%20variety%20of%20spaces.%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20the%20Beam%20supports%20decoding%20multi-channel%20audio%20formats%20with%20boisterous%20and%20vibrant%20performance%2C%20it%20doesn't%20feature%20any%20up-firing%20drivers.%20Instead%2C%20it%20relies%20on%20virtual%20processing%20to%20simulate%20a%20sense%20of%20overhead%20audio%20which%20just%20isn't%20as%20effective.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20you%20won't%20get%20the%20same%20kind%20of%20atmospheric%20overhead%20sound%20effects%20as%20you%20would%20on%20the%20more%20expensive%20Arc%20Ultra.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20movies%20sound%20immersive%2C%20and%20the%20Beam%20fills%20my%20space%20well%2C%20even%20when%20set%20to%20under%2050%25%20volume.%20%26quot%3BDune%26quot%3B%20is%20a%20great%20showcase%20for%20the%20Beam%2C%20with%20booming%20effects%20and%20a%20drum-heavy%20soundtrack%20that%20pounds%20along.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusic%20also%20sounds%20rich%20and%20full.%20It's%20impressive%20enough%20to%20serve%20as%20the%20DJ%20for%20home%20gatherings.%20Streaming%20music%20via%20WiFi%20through%20the%20Sonos%20app%20works%20well%20and%20encompasses%20a%20vast%20amount%20of%20services%2C%20but%20the%20soundbar%20also%20supports%20AirPlay%20for%20a%20more%20immediate%20listening%20experience.%20That%20said%2C%20like%20the%20Ray%2C%20the%20Beam%