a%20trip%20to%20Bengaluru%2C%20he%20met%20several%20farmers%20and%20learned%20about%20a%20unique%20variety%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F350000%2Fhow-to-grow-avocado-in-india-urban-farmer-harshit-godha-imports-saplings-from-israel-teaches-farming%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eavocados%3C%2Fa%3E%20called%20Arka%20Supreme.%20This%20variety%20caught%20his%20attention%20because%20it%20could%20adapt%20to%20Maharashtra%E2%80%99s%20hot%20climate%2C%20thriving%20even%20in%20temperatures%20as%20high%20as%2040%20to%2045%20degrees%20Celsius%20%E2%80%94%20perfect%20for%20Beed%E2%80%99s%20environment.%20%E2%80%9CArka%20Supreme%20is%20a%20high-yielding%20variety%2C%20and%20I%20knew%20it%20would%20work%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20confidently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20quest%20for%20knowledge%2C%20Parmeshwar%20visited%20the%20ICAR-Indian%20Institute%20of%20Horticultural%20Research%20(IIHR)%20in%20Bengaluru%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20avocado%20cultivation.%20There%2C%20he%20acquired%20valuable%20insights%20into%20farming%20practices.%20Equipped%20with%20this%20newfound%20knowledge%2C%20he%20ordered%2050%20avocado%20saplings%20from%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20starting%20avocado%20farming%20in%20Beed%20was%20far%20from%20easy.%20The%20region%20being%20notorious%20for%20its%20extreme%20temperatures%20and%20chronic%20water%20scarcity%2C%20the%20challenges%20initially%20seemed%20insurmountable%20for%20cultivating%20avocados.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20very%20little%20knowledge%20about%20avocado%20farming%20here%2C%20and%20no%20one%20had%20attempted%20it%20before%2C%E2%80%9D%20Parmeshwar%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20overcome%20these%20challenges%2C%20the%20first%20thing%20I%20did%20was%20dig%20two%20feet%20by%20two%20feet%20pits%20across%200.75%20acres%20of%20land%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CI%20filled%20them%20with%20cow%20dung%20manure%20before%20