ebareli-uttar-pradesh-anand-mishra-earning-five-times-more-in-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReturns%20from%20growing%20traditional%20crops%20were%20minimal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20input%20costs%20were%20high.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20traditional%20crops%20to%20dehydrated%20flowers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENishad%20began%20his%20venture%20with%20just%2010%20kg%20of%20dehydrated%20flowers%20and%20now%20sells%20between%2020%20and%2030%20tonnes%20annually%2C%20mostly%20sourced%20from%20Shekhpur%20and%20neighbouring%20villages.%20These%20villagers%20were%20traditionally%20growing%20crops%20like%20paddy%2C%20wheat%2C%20and%20lentils.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreviously%2C%20the%20sale%20of%20fresh%20flowers%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20lucrative%20enough%3B%20if%20they%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20sell%20them%2C%20the%20flowers%20would%20either%20be%20brought%20back%20home%20or%20discarded%20into%20the%20river.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F328701%2Fpunjab-farmer-starts-floriculture-exotic-flowers-help-earn-more-profits%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENishad%20convinced%20the%20farmers%20to%20grow%20these%20flowers%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20sell%20them%20to%20him.%20With%20his%20encouragement%2C%20the%20villagers%20took%20floriculture%20more%20seriously%20and%20now%20grow%20seven%20different%20varieties%20%E2%80%94%20Nishad%20purchases%20their%20entire%20harvest.%20The%20growers%20are%20paid%20promptly%20and%20no%20longer%20have%20to%20travel%2015%20km%20to%20the%20nearest%20%3Cem%3Emandi%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewith%20their%20produce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-3-1733937411.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22When%20Nishad%20switched%20to%20f