physical%20health%2C%20but%20it%20also%20helped%20us%20mentally%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20increased%20use%20of%20sanitary%20pads%20has%20fostered%20a%20more%20open%20dialogue%20about%20menstruation%2C%20even%20among%20men.%20This%20has%20led%20to%20a%20greater%20understanding%20of%20the%20challenges%20women%20face%2C%20creating%20a%20more%20supportive%20environment%20within%20households.%20As%20Soma%20joyfully%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20can%20now%20tell%20the%20men%20of%20our%20house%20that%20we%20need%20to%20buy%20sanitary%20napkins%2C%20and%20they%20go%2C%20buy%20napkins%20and%20give%20them%20to%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fwomen-participating-in-MHM-workshop-1-1733483695.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hands-on%20workshop%20conducted%20for%20the%20women%20regarding%20menstrual%20health%20management.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fwomen-participating-in-MHM-workshop-1-1733483695.jpg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fwomen-participating-in-MHM-workshop-1-1733483695-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fwomen-participating-in-MHM-workshop-1-1733483695-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fwomen-participating-in-MHM-workshop-1-1733483695-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fwomen-participating-in-MHM-workshop-1-1733483695-1200x900.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fwomen-participating-in-MHM-workshop-1-1733483695-800x600.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%